data.name: RibbonButtonSuperTip_Home
data.value: Qeda ukuphila kwesikole esisusa umphefumulo futhi ngaqonde phansi kwesigodlo se-Rizone! Chofoza ukuze uzungeze endlini yobuthakathaka bezinhlelo zokusebenza ze-Rizonesoft, lapho amahlambi amathikithi angafihliki futhi ahlabele ithebhisa lezinto zezwe.

data.name: Toast_LanguageChanged
data.value: Sibuyekezile ukubeka kwethu kwezilimi futhi sajikisa umlingiswa wokulingiswa kwezilimi ekwenzekeni kwakho kwe-Rizonesoft Office. Ukuqinisekisa ukuthi ukudlala kwethu kwamagama okuhlekisayo nokugxila okukhulumile akulahlekiswa kwihambo, sibonga uma uvala futhi izinhlelo ezivuliwe.

data.name: Language_DropDown_Error
data.value: Njengoba besakha imenyu yokukhetha ephikisayo, igremlin yedijithali yaqonda ukungena emphakathini ngaphandle kwemvite. Kodwa ungakhathazeki, ngoba ifayela lethu le-log elifanelekile likhombisa ingilazi yomhlahlandlela wokuhlolwa ukuthi ngubani ozimeleyo ngale mithwalo.

data.name: Language_CultureInfo_Error
data.value: Ekuqedeni kokugcina ulwazi lwethu lolimi, sifumanise ukuntuleka okungalindelekile kwematrikhisi. Ukuze siphendule le ngxoxo, siqhakambisa ukuchitha isikhathi kwifayela le-log elinemininingwane. Ngosizo lwakho, sizolungisa uchuku futhi siphucule ikhodi yethu ukuze sifinyelele isebenzisekiso esiqinile!

data.name: LoadLanguages_Error
data.value: Ulwazi lwethu lolimi lwathatha isikhathi esingalindelekile sokuphumula, sishiywa esimweni sesikhathi sonyaka sokukhuluma.

data.name: Toast_AppDataPathError
data.value: Siphuthukele emzalwanyweni wamatulisi lapho ukulayisha okulungiselelwe kwezinhlelo zethu kwakunabantu. Ungakhathazeki, sibhalile ngokucophelela lokhu okungalungile kwezakhiwo.

data.name: SettingsForm_LogFileLimit_ToolTip
data.value: Ukumisa ukuhlola kwezifayela zelogi kuyasisiza ukugcina indawo yethu yedijithali ephakeme. Lokhu kuncike kuhle kakhulu kuzivikela ukuthi asiphili ngokuphazima amafayela we-logi, silondoloze ubunye phakathi kwemfula engapheliyo yamaphuzu.

data.name: SettingsForm_Group_RollingInterval_ToolTip
data.value: Umklamo ongakhululeki, okhokhelwayo wamahora, uyabhala ingoma yezingqimba zezincwadi zemilayezo ezintsha. Ngokukhetha ukumisa 'Usuku', unika umhlobisi wezincwadi zemilayezo amandla okudala i-symphony entsha ngalinye ilanga - ngaphandle kokugwetshelwa, njengokufika kwakho kwesikhumulo sasekuseni.

data.name: SettingsForm_Button_OpenLog_ToolTip
data.value: Hamba phambili, umsebenzisi onobuntu, kulemikhaya yamafayela okubhalwa, lapho amazwana nezazi zokubhala zilindela ukubukwa kwakho okuhle.

data.name: SettingsForm_Button_CleanLog_TootlTip
data.value: Iminyaka isesifikile yokusetshenziswa kwamandla akho edijithali futhi ukucoca amalohgasi kucingweni lwe-Serilog. Kodwa qaphele le mikhumbi eyalulekayo - ngezindlela eziningi kubhekene nokubhekana nokubhatala.

data.name: SettingsForm_BtnOpenLog_ErrorMessage
data.value: Kutholakala ukuthi kukhona ukuhlukumeza okuncane, ngoba indlela yokufihla kwefayela yamalohgasi iya dlala umdlalo wokufihla nokuthola kwezintambo zedijithali.

data.name: SettingsForm_BtnCleanLog_Confirm_Message
data.value: Qina izikhali zakho bese ucinga ngokucophelela ngaphambi kokucindezela ukuthi 'susela' kulezi fayela zelogi. Khumbula ukuthi, njengendawo emnyama yedijithali, ukususa kuyiphiwe le ndawo yokubuya emuva; uma sekuphelile, kuyaphela kuze kube phakade.

data.name: SettingsForm_lblLocalDescription
data.value: Khetha ulimi kusuka ohlwini elikudaluhlangothi lwakho, bese ugcizelela amanxeba akho ukuthi abavikeli bethu benze umsebenzi wabo. Uma ulimi lwakho oluthandayo alukho, ungaqabali, ngoba sizokwanda izindlela zethu zokuxoxa ukulandelana kwalo esikhathini esingakude.
